              Eat a healthy meal before donating. Avoid fatty foods, such as hamburgers, french fries, or ice cream.<br>
              Drink plenty of water before donating.<br>
              Wear a shirt with roll-up sleeves.<br> .....</p>
            <a href="/users/servicesDetails" class="read-more"><span>Read More</span> <i
                class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
